icine practitioner (General Practice)&rdquo;或&ldquo;Registered Chinese medicine practitioner (Acupuncture)&rdquo;或&ldquo;Registered Chinese medicine practitioner (Bone-setting)&rdquo;;或以中文簡稱為&ldquo;註冊中醫(全科)&rdquo;或&ldquo;註冊中醫(針灸)&rdquo;或&ldquo;註冊中醫(骨傷)&rdquo;或&ldquo;註冊中醫師(全科)&rdquo;或&ldquo;註冊中醫師(針灸)&rdquo;或&ldquo;註冊中醫師(骨傷)&rdquo;(視屬何情況而定)。</blockquote></em>"},{"pid":"4c9a937d8a7e778275afbe0e317e2e23fafedfc7","tid":1933152,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c70a5d6b697c0d4e999355af5acafcaef3e4653","tid":1933152,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"807d8e1bc840ee81545ac5c3e7c293b8a27b3ad9","tid":1933152,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc8d888b09aacb453f6e8e7e3fc9987d5dc389e","tid":1933152,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"賓哥屎眼靚不？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"你把口好臭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"佩hack"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"使撚你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a153e5c4ccc9405a382f4d016277c3f1fe16c00","tid":1933152,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9a937d8a7e778275afbe0e317e2e23fafedfc7","tid":1933152,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c70a5d6b697c0d4e999355af5acafcaef3e4653","tid":1933152,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"807d8e1bc840ee81545ac5c3e7c293b8a27b3ad9","tid":1933152,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"你把口好臭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"佩hack"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"使撚你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"洗不洗貢講野"},{"pid":"be08bfd97cab1c1226928ca2e940b0c99e026cfb","tid":1933152,"uid":38189,"like